---
import SectionLabel from '../ui/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<section class="bg-warm-white px-8 py-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <SectionLabel>Who We Are</SectionLabel>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-[42px] font-medium text-ink leading-tight mb-4">
      Founded by researchers.<br/>Built for practitioners.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-14">
      Freyja Labs brings a rare combination: deep technical fluency in computing, AI, and engineering paired with rigorous pedagogical research and K&ndash;12 institutional knowledge.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-forest flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="font-serif text-[28px] text-warm-white font-semibold">MB</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-[26px] font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Mike Borowczak, Ph.D.</h3>
        <div class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-earth mb-4">Co-Founder</div>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
          Hardware security researcher and engineering educator. Directs a 50-member research lab with over $8M in funded projects spanning hardware security, AI/ML, and secure architectures. Editor-in-Chief of an engineering education journal. Translates complex technical content for audiences from elementary classrooms to corporate boardrooms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-forest flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="font-serif text-[28px] text-warm-white font-semibold">AB</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-serif text-[26px] font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Andrea C. Burrows Borowczak, Ed.D.</h3>
        <div class="font-mono text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-earth mb-4">Co-Founder</div>
        <p class="text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted">
          STEM education scholar and teacher preparation specialist. Directs a school of teacher education at a major research university. Principal investigator on multiple NSF-funded projects studying STEM integration and teacher preparation. National reputation in designing and delivering professional development that actually changes classroom practice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a href="/about" class="text-forest font-medium text-[15px] hover:text-forest-dark transition-colors">
        Learn more about us &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
